{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-valentine-berhenti-tayang-ini-penjelasannya/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Film Valentine Berhenti Tayang! Ini Penjelasannya.","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beruntunglah bro sis yang sudah sempat menonton film Valentine, karena sejak tanggal 25 November 2017 kemarin film tersebut diberhentikan penayangannya di bioskop-bioskop 21 maupun non 21 (CGV, Cinemaxx dan lainnya). Pihak Skylar Picture memberikan penjelasan bahwa mereka tidak ingin mengecewakan masyarakat dengan hasil karya yang menjadi <em>project</em> ambisius pihak Skylar Picture tersebut.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_30167\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30167\" data-attachment-id=\"30167\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-valentine-berhenti-tayang-ini-penjelasannya/attachment/1-185/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;SMPN 170&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1512039017&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : instagram @skylar.picture)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : instagram @skylar.picture)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1-10.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1-10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-30167\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1-10.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : instagram @skylar.picture)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-30167\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : instagram @skylar.picture)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Skylar picture juga meminta maaf atas penarikan film superhero tersebut melalui akun Instagram dan Facebooknya. Film ini telah dikerjakan selama hampir 3 tahun, pra poduksi sejak tahun 2014 dan pengambilan gambar selama 121 hari sejak bulan Februari 2015 sampai September 2015, dan pasca produksi dilakukan hampir 2 tahun. Pada bulan Desember 2016, Skylar Picture mulai mengerjakan CGI (Computer Generated Image) bersama EPIX Studio. Namun pada bulan Agustus 2017, <em>hardisk</em> atau <em>server</em> EPIX Studio tersebut <em>crash </em>saat pihak Skylar Picture sudah menerima tanggal tayang film Valentine dari bioskop 21 yaitu pada tanggal 23 November 2017.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_30176\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30176\" data-attachment-id=\"30176\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-valentine-berhenti-tayang-ini-penjelasannya/attachment/poster/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/POSTER.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;SMPN 170&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1510315511&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/POSTER.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/POSTER.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-30176\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/POSTER.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-30176\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Karena hal tersebut, Skylar Picture terpaksa mengerjakan proses CGI selama 2,5 bulan, yang seharusnya proses tersebut dikerjakan selama 10 bulan. Dilema bagi pihak Skylar Picture antara tetap menayangkan film tersebut atau mundur. Namun mereka mengambil keputusan untuk tetap menayangkan film Valentine dengan segala kekurangannya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_30182\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30182\" data-attachment-id=\"30182\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-valentine-berhenti-tayang-ini-penjelasannya/attachment/wawan/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/WAWAN.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;SMPN 170&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1510314978&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/WAWAN.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/WAWAN.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-30182\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/WAWAN.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-30182\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_30173\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30173\" data-attachment-id=\"30173\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-valentine-berhenti-tayang-ini-penjelasannya/attachment/4-1-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/4-1-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;SMPN 170&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1512039650&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/4-1-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/4-1-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-30173\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/4-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-30173\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Penarikan film Valentine memang sangat disayangkan, melihat sedikit sekali film Indonesia yang memiliki genre superhero. Aswin M.C. Siregar selaku produser film ini pun memiliki keinginan agar film Valentine bisa kembali tayang di bioskop-bioskop Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_30170\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-30170\" data-attachment-id=\"30170\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-valentine-berhenti-tayang-ini-penjelasannya/attachment/2-1-34/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;SMPN 170&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1512039368&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-30170\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-30170\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : Instagram @valentinemovie)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Film Valentine sendiri menceritakan tentang kisah yang berlatar belakang di kota Batavia City, kota indah yang tak lagi aman dihuni. Perampokan, kekerasan, dan berbagai kriminalitas semakin hari semakin merajalela. Di tengah kota yang kacau ini, Srimaya, seorang pelayan kafe yang memiliki mimpi menjadi aktris tidak pernah menyangka kalau impiannya akan mengubah jalan hidupnya. Pertemuannya dengan seorang sutradara film dan sahabatnya, Bono dan Wawan, akan membawanya pada petualangan berbahaya penuh aksi mendebarkan dengan nyawa sebagai taruhannya. Mengubahnya dari gadis biasa menjadi pahlawan harapan Batavia City, Valentine, yang bertugas membasmi kejahatan. Semoga akan ada kabar baik terkait film Valentine ini ya, bro sis!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"cb4095c0-bd50-5b98-9836-41865f856c60"}}}